We need a spa vacation not only for treatment, but also for the prevention of diseases.
In a sanatorium, a person can check the state of his body and receive doctor&#39;s recommendations on how to live so that his health does not deteriorate.
Such recommendations will not be superfluous to anyone.
“I’m just tired of work” is an important signal from the body and should not be dismissed.
Constant stress, mental and physical fatigue can lead to depression and chronic fatigue syndrome.
And stress is experienced by about 90% of visitors.
Moreover, people from large cities aged 45 to 55 are most susceptible to it.
So it&#39;s best not to complicate the situation and give yourself a break in time.
Studies show that 98% of people reduce their biological age during their stay in a sanatorium.
Modern sanatoriums offer a comfortable stay for the whole family.
So, if you want to spend a vacation with children, you do not have to part with them.
Wellness programs are provided for children, even the smallest ones, which include both diagnostic services, pediatrician consultations, analyzes, and medical ones.
For example, swimming (in many resorts there are children&#39;s pools), inhalation, a special diet, massages, oxygen cocktails, physiotherapy exercises.
