We will extend fruiting.
What can be done to keep the harvest until the end of the season?
By Yulia Belopukhova, agronomist and summer resident.
It&#39;s time for tall tomatoes to get a haircut: remove new stepchildren, cut off the tops, remove all leaves until the penultimate brush with fruits and inflorescences with small ovaries - they will not have time to ripen.
All tomatoes, regardless of their &quot;constitution&quot;, as well as peppers and eggplants, are fed with ash-superphosphate extract, treated with biological products (Dosrevatel - to accelerate the filling and growth of fruits, Fitosporin-M, Fitolavin, Gamair, Bactofit - from diseases, Immunocytofit - to increase immunity, Bitoxybacillin, Lepidocid, Fitoverm - if there are pests).
Of the chemicals at the end of summer, it is worth using only copper sulfate, colloidal sulfur and green soap.
We do the last watering of the plants.
