Transport tax notifications will no longer be sent by mail - Behind the wheel website www.zr.ru
The tax office has changed the procedure for sending notifications about property taxes.
All Russian car owners are accustomed to a scheme that has not changed over the years: in the summer and autumn, they receive receipts by mail for payment of the transport tax for the previous year.
However, many will not wait for them this year.
The fact is that the tax office quietly changed the procedure for notifying citizens.
Those who are registered in the &quot;Personal account of the taxpayer&quot; on the official website of the department nalog.ru will receive notifications in electronic form.
The inspectorate automatically considered such Russians to be online users and deleted them from the standard, &quot;paper&quot; mailing list.
The innovation will affect all owners of vehicles and real estate.
Everyone else will continue to receive their usual letters.
However, owners of an account on the site also have the opportunity to return to the old scheme.
To do this, they will have to visit the tax office during August and write a statement.
On the one hand, the new order is more modern and more convenient.
The notification will appear in the &quot;personal account&quot; immediately after compilation, while the letter will take several days and may be completely lost.
In addition, the number of users of the Internet service of the tax inspectorate has exceeded 18 million, which will allow the department to seriously save on mailing.
On the other hand, modest news on the site of the inspection is clearly not enough to inform citizens about the changed order.
Some could register in a &quot;personal account&quot; to receive a one-time service and have long forgotten about it.
These people will not wait for notifications by mail and, without knowing it, will fall into the category of non-payers with all the ensuing consequences.
Access to the &quot;Personal account of the taxpayer&quot; is carried out in three ways: through the account of the gosuslugi.ru portal, using an electronic signature or entering the login and password specified in the registration card.
The latter can be obtained in person at any tax office (regardless of the place of registration).
We remind you that this year the transport tax must be paid by December 1.
Distribution of notifications began in July.
